    {
        "sha": "628b3e80c9f0be2ae3d863aa81d11faa44edc44e",
        "author": "JEECG",
        "email": "445654970@qq.com",
        "date": "2026-07-13T04:41:34Z",
        "message": "--author:JEECG--date:20260713--for:【vite8】消除 dev server 启动时两条 WARN（esbuildOptions 废弃、esbuild/oxc 同时设置）\n\n按 Vite 8 Rolldown/Oxc 的迁移规范，把两处已废弃的 esbuild 配置迁到新写法：\n\n1. optimizeDeps.esbuildOptions.target: 'es2020' → optimizeDeps.rolldownOptions.transform.target: 'es2020'\n   （消除 esbuildOptions deprecated 警告）\n\n2. 顶层 esbuild: { drop: isBuild ? ['console', 'debugger'] : [] } + build.minify: 'esbuild'\n   → 删除 esbuild 块，build.minify: true 改用 Oxc minifier，\n   drop 功能迁移到 build.rollupOptions.output.minify: { compress: { drop: ['console', 'debugger'] } }\n   （消除 esbuild/oxc 同时设置的警告，并保留生产构建删除 console.debugger 的能力）",
        "url": "https://github.com/jeecgboot/JeecgBoot/commit/628b3e80c9f0be2ae3d863aa81d11faa44edc44e"
    },
